{"tid":430422,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺笑波子啲片其實幾好笑","createTime":"2017-10-09T18:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T09:39:42.000Z","uid":54791,"like":770,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0b374ce42a58aa5c783b1009923d915d107310","tid":430422,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"望住一個低質youtuber玩cuphead係到鳩叫<br />\n真係笑撚到我流眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正正常常打機應該好少出聲<br />\n而呢一班低質youtuber永遠打機好似鬥大聲咁，講嘅野仲要冇經過大腦咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚野小蜜蜂嗡嗡嗡呀?乜撚野等我射爆佢呀?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講野可唔可以有返啲邏輯呀?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相比之下，伍公子玩cuphead真係唔錯<br />\n起碼人地講嘅野經過大腦，做下功課又講返啲趣聞，而唔係無腦鳩叫<br />\n伍公子/達哥未必有資格上到神台<br />\n但係對呢群on9仔一早已經超晒班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奈何新一代觀眾大部分都係小學雞，一早比你班呃飯食嘅撚樣洗撚晒腦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人玩cuphead你就跟人地玩cuphead</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人地開live都好撚過你拍video，人地冇得edit㗎柒頭皮</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係你就收收皮，學下點樣講野有條理先再呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa9223a218be32f9f404b5af8d63fda95fb368b","tid":430422,"uid":16330,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"佢把聲真係好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老母成個戇鳩仔咁<br />\n成撚日喺到muffin muffin<br />\n啲小學雞fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ccac9424e3a7f39bd3000c1e6b755d7da549ec","tid":430422,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 369"},{"pid